{"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation"]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)showsUserLocation","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L590"},"symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"showsUserLocation","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Setting this property to ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the "},{"code":"userLocationVisible","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Your app must specify a value for ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription"},{"text":" or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription"},{"text":" in its ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Info.plist"},{"text":" to satisfy the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"requirements of the underlying Core Location framework when enabling this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you implement a custom location manager, set the "},{"code":"locationManager","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling "},{"code":"showsUserLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location."}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/Map